name: Egg holder, vintage ceramic cup, japan, face, brown, kitchen, gempo
description:
This is a listing for one: Egg holder, vintage ceramic cup, japan, face, brown, kitchen

I'm an avid egg cups collector and this is definitely one of my favourites. It's a very simple scandinavian look egg holder of a persons torso. It looks like a child. It's originally made by a Japanese company named Gempo.
 
It's in a very good vintage shape. The top part has a matte finish, the bottom part is glazed. 

It has been placed in a dishwasher and seems to come out good. To keep it in good shape for a long time it's better to wash it by hand.

name: Macbook sleeve, grey winter colours, forest style, 13 inch
description:
Macbook sleeve, grey winter colours, forest style, 13 inch

This knitted laptop sleeve and knitted MacBook sleeve is colourful and unique. The sleeve is custom made for your 13'' MacBook Air or MacBook Pro.

The sleeve is knitted with several layers of thick yarn and thick needles to make the look a bit different. The sleeve is made in one piece out of mostly acrylic yarn and has a tight fit. In this way the laptop sleeve stays in it's place, although the sleeve is open on one side.

The sleeve is delivered with an elastic that can be used optionally for extra security. It can be placed horizontally around the sleeve (see pictures other listings). 

The sleeve is made in a smoke and pet free free home.
Colors may differ slightly because of photography and computer projection.

********************************************

The sleeve should be washed on a low temperature because it contains some wool in some cases, depending on the sleeve.

name: Shiny golden, Cupcake toppers, Party Supplies, birthday decor, 20pcs
description:
Shiny golden, Cupcake toppers, Party Supplies, birthday decor, 20pcs

These cupcake toppers are a great addition to wedding, birthday, baby shower or any other party. These silver flags are all in one shiny colour. They can be used on top of cup cakes or as decoration on a gift.

The flags are all attached wooden toothpick and come in a package of 20. You can also give them as a gift as they come perfectly packed as a little gift.

You can combine them perfectly with many other paper goods of my shop. I have these picks in gold as well, please have a look at my other listings.

These picks are no toys, so please keep them away from small children :)
